2- Conjuration is the power to call forth unearthy creatures such as demons into our world by means of sorcery. It includes summonings spells;
3 - Transmutation involves a mutating force which alters substances from one shape or form to another. Such forms include changing metals into gold and transforming living creatures into something other than they started out as.;
